    {
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**tatara-chat** business + readiness + HTTP metrics, all pinned to `job=\"tatara-chat\"` (names like `panics_total`, `http_requests_total`, and `readyz_*` collide across components, so every query pins the job). Live today: `chat_active_rooms`, `chat_polls_total`, `chat_store_duration_seconds`, `chat_sweeper_runs_total`, and the `readyz_*` probe trio. Message/room/participant/handoff/store-error/sweeper-error/auth/panic/HTTP series are wired but 0-series until chat gets real client traffic - empty panels below are expected, not broken queries. `/healthz`, `/readyz`, and `/metrics` never enter `http_requests_total` (excluded producer-side in internal/httpapi/router.go), so the HTTP panels below need no extra route filtering to stay probe-clean; the 5xx ratio panel still carries a defensive `route!~` filter to match the deployed alert convention used elsewhere in this repo."
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "description": "Active chat rooms, sampled by the sweeper (chat_active_rooms). Live today. Sparkline shows the trend over the dashboard window.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "mappings": [],
          "min": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 3},
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "chat_active_rooms{job=\"tatara-chat\"}",
          "legendFormat": "active rooms",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Active Rooms",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "description": "Readiness flap history: episodes where /readyz flipped the pod NotReady over the last 15m (increase of readyz_not_ready_total). A DB blip flips the probe by design; a non-zero here is the readiness-flap signal, correlate with store errors below.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "mappings": [],
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "red", "value": 1}]}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 3},
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum (increase(readyz_not_ready_total{job=\"tatara-chat\"}[15m]))",
          "legendFormat": "not-ready flips (15m)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Readiness Flips (15m)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "description": "Readiness ping failure ratio: rate(readyz_failures_total) / rate(readyz_checks_total), denominator clamped so an idle service reads 0 rather than NaN. Sustained elevation means the DB dependency behind /readyz is unhealthy. Live today.",
